<br>
But are there any known &quot;hidden&quot; merits of agility?<br>
<br>
Chubb asked could there be a possible difference between 1250 ac at 100 agi and 1250 agi at 255.<br>
<br>
I've heard a mumble or two about agi effecting dodge/parry/riposte...but not really how, haven't done any of my own research on it and got kinda curious. <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=3362" target="_blank">Veteran Flelemph Morianstone</a><br>
"What?! Now you've done it! The bunnies are angry! ANGRY I TELL YOU!"
