<br>
Not getting hit at all &gt;&gt;&gt; getting hit for less damage.<br>
<br>
The only problem is that AGI is capped at 255, but you can still keep adding mitigation AC. <p><A href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=14686"> Graal MacBladefury</A><BR>
